text: Väinö Tiihonen (28 November 1912 - 27 July 1957) was a Finnish ski jumper. He competed in the individual event at the 1936 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1912 births Category:1957 deaths Category:Finnish male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Finland Category:Ski jumpers at the 1936 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Helsinki
